{"ts":"2026-04-15T06:56:19.024Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":1406,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"// Remove URP/Lit from Always Included Shaders (too many variants)\nvar assets = UnityEditor.AssetDatabase.LoadAllAssetsAtPath(\"ProjectSettings/GraphicsSettings.asset\");\nvar so = new UnityEditor.SerializedObject(assets[0]);\nvar always = so.FindProperty(\"m_AlwaysIncludedShaders\");\nvar urpLit = UnityEngine.Shader.Find(\"Universal Render Pipeline/Lit\");\nint removed = 0;\nfor (int i = always.arraySize - 1; i >= 0; i--) {\n    var el = always.GetArrayElementAtIndex(i).objectReferenceValue;\n    if (el == urpLit) {\n        always.DeleteArrayElementAtIndex(i);\n        removed++;\n    }\n}\nso.ApplyModifiedProperties();\nUnityEditor.AssetDatabase.SaveAssets();\n\n// List current contents for verification\nstring s = \"removedLit=\"+removed+\"\\nAlwaysIncluded now:\\n\";\nfor (int i = 0; i < always.arraySize; i++) {\n    var el = always.GetArrayElementAtIndex(i).objectReferenceValue;\n    s += \"  \"+i+\": \"+(el!=null?el.name:\"NULL\")+\"\\n\";\n}\nreturn s;","safety_checks":false,"compiler":"auto"}}
