{"ts":"2026-04-15T07:10:24.430Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":9373,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"// Scan a scene YAML for all m_Script GUIDs and validate each against AssetDatabase.\nstring path = \"H:/fight-for-life-unity/Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\";\nstring text = System.IO.File.ReadAllText(path);\nvar rx = new System.Text.RegularExpressions.Regex(@\"m_Script:\\s*\\{fileID:\\s*(-?\\d+),\\s*guid:\\s*([0-9a-fA-F]{32}),\\s*type:\\s*(\\d+)\\}\");\nvar matches = rx.Matches(text);\nvar brokenGuids = new System.Collections.Generic.HashSet<string>();\nint totalMB = 0;\nforeach (System.Text.RegularExpressions.Match m in matches) {\n    totalMB++;\n    string guid = m.Groups[2].Value;\n    string apath = UnityEditor.AssetDatabase.GUIDToAssetPath(guid);\n    if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(apath) || !System.IO.File.Exists(System.IO.Path.GetFullPath(apath))) {\n        brokenGuids.Add(guid);\n    }\n}\nstring s = \"totalMBRefs=\"+totalMB+\" brokenGuids=\"+brokenGuids.Count+\"\\n\";\nforeach (var g in brokenGuids) s += \"  broken=\"+g+\"\\n\";\nreturn s;","safety_checks":false,"compiler":"auto"}}
