{"ts":"2026-04-15T08:47:52.830Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":3135,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"// Bisect: open Island_Flood, clone first half into new scene, check format\nUnityEditor.EditorSettings.serializationMode = UnityEditor.SerializationMode.ForceText;\nvar src = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n    \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single);\nvar roots = src.GetRootGameObjects();\nint half = roots.Length / 2;\n\n// Test 1: first half\nvar dst = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.NewScene(\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.NewSceneSetup.EmptyScene,\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.NewSceneMode.Additive);\nfor (int i = 0; i < half; i++) {\n    var c = UnityEngine.Object.Instantiate(roots[i]);\n    c.name = roots[i].name;\n    UnityEngine.SceneManagement.SceneManager.MoveGameObjectToScene(c, dst);\n}\nstring p1 = \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/PROBE_FIRST_HALF.unity\";\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveScene(dst, p1, false);\nbyte[] h = new byte[2];\nusing (var fs = System.IO.File.OpenRead(p1)) { fs.Read(h, 0, 2); }\nbool firstIsText = h[0]=='%';\nlong firstSize = new System.IO.FileInfo(p1).Length;\n\n// Reload src for second test\nsrc = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n    \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single);\nroots = src.GetRootGameObjects();\nvar dst2 = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.NewScene(\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.NewSceneSetup.EmptyScene,\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.NewSceneMode.Additive);\nfor (int i = half; i < roots.Length; i++) {\n    var c = UnityEngine.Object.Instantiate(roots[i]);\n    c.name = roots[i].name;\n    UnityEngine.SceneManagement.SceneManager.MoveGameObjectToScene(c, dst2);\n}\nstring p2 = \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/PROBE_SECOND_HALF.unity\";\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveScene(dst2, p2, false);\nusing (var fs = System.IO.File.OpenRead(p2)) { fs.Read(h, 0, 2); }\nbool secondIsText = h[0]=='%';\nlong secondSize = new System.IO.FileInfo(p2).Length;\n\nreturn \"totalRoots=\"+roots.Length+\" half=\"+half+\n       \" | firstHalf isText=\"+firstIsText+\" size=\"+firstSize+\n       \" | secondHalf isText=\"+secondIsText+\" size=\"+secondSize;","safety_checks":false,"compiler":"auto"}}
