{"ts":"2026-04-15T08:48:11.399Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":3637,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"// Bisect first half: 0-18 vs 19-37\nUnityEditor.EditorSettings.serializationMode = UnityEditor.SerializationMode.ForceText;\nint lo = 0, hi = 38;\n\nwhile (hi - lo > 1) {\n    int mid = (lo + hi) / 2;\n    var src = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n        \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n        UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single);\n    var roots = src.GetRootGameObjects();\n    var dst = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.NewScene(\n        UnityEditor.SceneManagement.NewSceneSetup.EmptyScene,\n        UnityEditor.SceneManagement.NewSceneMode.Additive);\n    // Try [lo, mid)\n    for (int i = lo; i < mid; i++) {\n        var c = UnityEngine.Object.Instantiate(roots[i]);\n        c.name = roots[i].name;\n        UnityEngine.SceneManagement.SceneManager.MoveGameObjectToScene(c, dst);\n    }\n    string p = \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/PROBE_BS.unity\";\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveScene(dst, p, false);\n    byte[] h = new byte[2];\n    using (var fs = System.IO.File.OpenRead(p)) { fs.Read(h, 0, 2); }\n    bool isText = h[0] == '%';\n    if (isText) {\n        // [lo, mid) is fine, problem is in [mid, hi)\n        lo = mid;\n    } else {\n        // Problem is in [lo, mid)\n        hi = mid;\n    }\n}\n\n// Now lo is the index of the problematic root. Get its name.\nvar src2 = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n    \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single);\nvar rootsFinal = src2.GetRootGameObjects();\nstring offender = \"<oob>\";\nif (lo < rootsFinal.Length) offender = rootsFinal[lo].name;\nreturn \"culpritIndex=\"+lo+\" name=\"+offender;","safety_checks":false,"compiler":"auto"}}
