{"ts":"2026-04-15T09:15:51.895Z","tool":"execute_code","type":"tool","status":"SUCCESS","ms":1595,"action":"execute","params":{"action":"execute","code":"// Save current state, remove Terrain from Island_Flood, rebuild\nvar scn = UnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.OpenScene(\n    \"Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n    UnityEditor.SceneManagement.OpenSceneMode.Single);\nvar roots = scn.GetRootGameObjects();\nUnityEngine.GameObject terrain = null;\nforeach (var r in roots) {\n    if (r.GetComponent<UnityEngine.Terrain>() != null) { terrain = r; break; }\n}\nstring before = \"terrain=\"+(terrain==null?\"NOT FOUND\":terrain.name);\nif (terrain == null) return before;\n\n// Backup the scene as a copy first\nSystem.IO.File.Copy(\"H:/fight-for-life-unity/Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.unity\",\n                    \"H:/fight-for-life-unity/Assets/_FightForLife/Scenes/Island_Flood.bak\",\n                    true);\n\n// Replace Terrain with a simple ground plane at same position\nvar plane = UnityEngine.GameObject.CreatePrimitive(UnityEngine.PrimitiveType.Plane);\nplane.name = \"Ground_Replacement\";\nplane.transform.position = terrain.transform.position;\nplane.transform.localScale = new UnityEngine.Vector3(200, 1, 200);\nUnityEngine.SceneManagement.SceneManager.MoveGameObjectToScene(plane, scn);\n\nUnityEngine.Object.DestroyImmediate(terrain);\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.MarkSceneDirty(scn);\nUnityEditor.SceneManagement.EditorSceneManager.SaveScene(scn);\n\nreturn before+\" | terrain removed, plane added\";","safety_checks":false,"compiler":"auto"}}
